title: Toncoin, Uniswap holders rush Kelexo as presale gains momentum
description: Amidst the evolving market of cryptocurrency, Kelexo (KLXO) has emerged as a beacon of innovation, attracting attention from Toncoin (TON) and Uniswap (UNI) holders alike.

title: DeeStream gains traction as TRX and ETH surge; SHIB gains 230%
description: The market surge that the crypto industry is experiencing has had ripple effects on Web3 projects such as DeeStream (DST). Investor whales in projects such as Tron (TRX) and Ethereum (ETH) want to expand their portfolio. DeeStream (DST) is the project with promise as it's speculated to go up 20x its presale value as Shiba Inu (SHIB) surges 230%.
